00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:38,163
that was built around these sort of semi-procedural runs

261
00:15:38,163 --> 00:15:40,124
where you set up your equipment, you go,

262
00:15:40,124 --> 00:15:41,945
and then either see how far you can get

