00:15:41,945 --> 00:15:44,706
or go until you die.

264
00:15:44,706 --> 00:15:48,328
So the only thing we could figure out

265
00:15:48,328 --> 00:15:50,389
was that it's kind of like Desert Strike,

266
00:15:50,389 --> 00:15:52,410
kind of like Crusader, no remorse.

